# Deployment Protection

- These files are sensitive and affect Coolify deployment.
- Do not change ports, domains, base images, or build logic casually.
- Any edit here must consider staging, production, and environment variables.
- Prefer minimal, explicit, justified changes.
- Flag rollout risk before changing deployment-sensitive behavior.
